  "body": "As a user\r\nI want to be able to @everyone mention in a community\r\nSo that I can notify everyone\r\n\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nWhen typing @ev.. in the autocomplete for mention, there should be an option to mention everyone. \r\n\r\nA lot of mention code should be ported in status go for compatibility with desktop, so as a part of this feature, I'd suggest creating an endpoint (if it doesn't exist already and desktop uses it), to suggest mentions based on some text in status-go.\r\n\r\nFeel free to ping me so we can have a chat before starting on this issue.",
